title: Tide | Tide Pod Challenge: Rooster Teeth Makes a Little Mess
description:
►Stay up-to-date with all of the latest videos by subscribing to our channel right here: https://www.youtube.com/user/tidelaundry/?sub_confirmation=1      

In this Rooster Teeth short, we watch Brandon and Blaine take the Tide Pod Challenge (or as they would call it, the “T-Chall”) by convincing their fellow Rooster Teeth member Barbara, to participate in a “little” messy fun.
